items.sentence: I didn't think Tom would be in Australia this week.
I didn't think that Tom had ever been to Australia.
I didn't know Tom was going to Australia with Mary.
I didn't know that Tom was in Australia last month.
I love the fuzzy feeling I get when I help someone.
The firefighters are still searching for survivors.
No one can make me do something I don't want to do.
Had it not been for your help, I would have failed.
We certainly hope that's not going to happen again.
Many people think that that isn't likely to happen.
